@startuml
title Diagrama de clases - Entidades principales (Gasolineras Project)

' Clases principales
class User {
  +UUID id
  +String email
  +String password_hash
  +String name
  +String role
  +boolean is_active
  +timestamptz created_at
  +timestamptz updated_at
  +timestamptz last_login
}

class Favorite {
  +UUID id
  +UUID user_id
  +UUID gas_station_id
  +String note
  +timestamptz created_at
}

class GasStation {
  +UUID id
  +String external_id
  +String name
  +String brand
  +String address
  +String city
  +String province
  +String postal_code
  +double lat
  +double lon
  +JSONB metadata
  +String source
  +timestamptz created_at
  +timestamptz updated_at
  +timestamptz last_fetched_at
}

class Price {
  +UUID id
  +UUID gas_station_id
  +String fuel_type
  +Numeric price
  +String currency
  +timestamptz observed_at
  +timestamptz created_at
}

class Prediction {
  +UUID id
  +UUID gas_station_id
  +String fuel_type
  +Numeric predicted_price
  +Date predicted_for
  +String model_version
  +JSONB features
  +int horizon
  +Numeric confidence
  +timestamptz created_at
}

class EVChargingStation {
  +UUID id
  +String external_id
  +JSONB data
  +double lat
  +double lon
  +String source
  +timestamptz last_fetched_at
}

' Relaciones
User "1" -- "*" Favorite : has
Favorite "*" --> "1" GasStation : references
GasStation "1" -- "*" Price : has
GasStation "1" -- "*" Prediction : has
GasStation "0..1" -- "0..*" EVChargingStation : optional_cache

' Notas
note right of GasStation
  - metadata almacena horarios y servicios (JSONB)
  - Para búsquedas por proximidad usar PostGIS (location GEOGRAPHY(POINT,4326))
end note

note left of Price
  - Mantener histórico: una fila por observación (observed_at)
  - Considerar particionado por fecha si escala mucho
end note

note right of Prediction
  - Guardar model_version y features para reproducibilidad
  - Alternativa: cache en Redis para predicciones en tiempo real
end note

' Leyenda simple
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

@enduml
